{"tid":363913,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人內向啲但另一半好outgoing？","createTime":"2017-08-18T03:32:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T12:30:50.000Z","uid":110075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1848ff15662c69d5e8d400342f61c358efd9cf9c","tid":363913,"uid":110075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T03:32:30.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我份人慢熱啲但另一半好外向好易識人有好多朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家佢出左嚟做嘢，1-5已經要翻工，放工有時又踢波，又成日會約唔同gp嘅fd食飯，佢見幾個gp d fd嘅時間仲多過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺佢嘅人生太豐富喇，我只係佔佢心中好少嘅位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我知實有人叫我搵下興趣搵多啲嘢做下，但我覺得佢已經咁忙我仲填滿自己時間，咁之後咪仲難約佢仲難見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲，你地有冇類似情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a4d5e8736bb1909c0d64a09943fec5802582c3","tid":363913,"uid":74397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:20:38.000Z","msg":"鐘意佢啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca0aecca81bf0c118822d8b5a1fdfebd7253164","tid":363913,"uid":111243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T07:41:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67cef4ea420b4e722263b996022219f7ef4dcd30","tid":363913,"uid":28221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T07:44:19.000Z","msg":"同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同佢反映下 或者跟埋佢一齊出席活動"},{"pid":"60e70cb762386bb7349c2b30c615f183c04dab6e","tid":363913,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T08:12:45.000Z","msg":"試過同外向撚拍拖 我本身比較慢熱同鍾意靜 <br />\n但佢就日日有聚會同朋友玩 鍾意多人熱鬧<br />\n結論性格南轅北轍通常八成散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6abe0d80f5d04582beec9f338ed1a599aeded09","tid":363913,"uid":110075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T09:28:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鐘意佢啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n份人幾幽默，對我都幾好平時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f5afee1b71e35884669420dc05b207194b5996","tid":363913,"uid":110075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T09:30:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n[member]我宜家都驚佢會覺我成日chur佢見面，所以唔敢主動話要見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但咁落去我都驚感情變淡 可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ［/member]"},{"pid":"5803cf6ee4011349a576ae6d67635cb0658236de","tid":363913,"uid":110075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T09:32:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同佢反映下 或者跟埋佢一齊出席活動</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n反映過啦佢會話我唔識佢啲fd 到時會好尷尬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講講下我都唔敢問，怕佢會覺我chur住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97eacb3aba8ffcbb8d0ad7c6709005a472b1d0b","tid":363913,"uid":110075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T09:34:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過同外向撚拍拖 我本身比較慢熱同鍾意靜 <br />\n但佢就日日有聚會同朋友玩 鍾意多人熱鬧<br />\n結論性格南轅北轍通常八成散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同佢一齊咗好多年，其他相處都好好唔想就咁散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f1ed077a47379465f73ffd487bc4884445f88e","tid":363913,"uid":117238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T09:36:27.000Z","msg":"我係絲 掉返轉<br />\n男朋友好外向痴身鐘意周圍去<br />\n我比較獨立鐘意靜 摺係屋企hea下享受放假既寧靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家熱戀期...佢隔一兩日就想見面出去玩 搞到我都唔知點好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8818d753ca44b4c0e54a0efe3fe9a1731dc9d405","tid":363913,"uid":132736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T09:39:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我份人慢熱啲但另一半好外向好易識人有好多朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家佢出左嚟做嘢，1-5已經要翻工，放工有時又踢波，又成日會約唔同gp嘅fd食飯，佢見幾個gp d fd嘅時間仲多過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺佢嘅人生太豐富喇，我只係佔佢心中好少嘅位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我知實有人叫我搵下興趣搵多啲嘢做下，但我覺得佢已經咁忙我仲填滿自己時間，咁之後咪仲難約佢仲難見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲，你地有冇類似情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己就內外向活動都有，但ex係超外向每日都要新鮮感有唔同活動鍾意出去同人玩唔同野，最後佢覺得完全夾唔到，已分手。"},{"pid":"bba078e5ac6fa82a22f295a4da5c6472f9bbc961","tid":363913,"uid":111243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T12:30:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}